= title "Selected works"
= description "Some of the work I've done the past few years."
%section.headline_box.projects_page
  .mask
  
%main
  .row 
    %section.primary_information 
      %h2 Projects 
      %hr
      %p
        :markdown
          Throughout the calendar year, in-between my universites duties that are now behind me, I've worked on a variety of projects. From websites to native web applications, I've been busy. The following projects I've done in the past that I can publicly disclose. 

          **Note: I'm temporarily displaced; will update this project with more work I can publically disclose after I have time to aquire them.** 

      .list_of_projects_wrapper.masonry-container
        = render @projects || content_tag(:p, markdown.render("Have no projects publically visible at the moment or there's a server problem I'll address shortly.") )

    %aside.complimentary_information 

      %section.related_skills  
        %h2 Skills Most Showcased  
        %hr
        = content_tag(:p, markdown.render("There seems to be no clear way to sort out the skills most utilized at the moment, there's no projects publically available for this to be relevant, or I have some algorithms changing to do...").html_safe ) unless render partial: 'technologies/technology_showcased', collection: @most_showcased_skills, as: :technology
